<br>
I was getting a spell in Iceclad lastnight and did this quest. Pretty easy to do, just gave him the stuff and new mask.<br>
Best thing is it gave me like +13 AC on my stats. figure that out. <br>
(Spoiler below) <br>
Here is what i followed. Make sure nothing is stacked and i bought one component at Igloos for 6gp.<br>
<br>
Cougarskin Mask <br>
MAGIC ITEM NO DROP <br>
AC: +6 Agi: +2 Dex: +2 HP: +10 <br>
Weight: 1.0 <br>
Classes: Ranger Shaman Druid Cleric Paladin Shadowknight Bard Monk Rogue Warrior <br>
Races: Iksar Dwarf Gnome Dark Elf Barbarian Erudite Halfling Wood Elf High Elf Half Elf Human <br>
<br>
<br>
The mammoth meat you can get from hunting mammoths in EW! This might seem a little too obvious for some people, but you don't need to go to Halas to get mammoth meat. (On the other hand, if you're coming from there, by all means, buy some mam-meat and you're ready to go.) We had a group 30-38 hunting &quot;wildlife&quot; by the EW/IO bridge to complete the shawl quests, and we killed a few mammoths, the meat was easy to get. You might even be able to buy it off the igloo guys if somebody sold them theirs. <br>
<br>
You go to Ergrez Shortpaw (not Ergriz, his helper without a last name) and hail him. He is located in the gnoll camp SE of the Tower of Frozen Shadow. The gnolls in this camp are indifferent and do not seem to be KOS; I walked right into camp w/out sow on and was not attacked. He will tell you something about how he's the tailor for his clan, etc., and will say how he can make armor if you tell him what you have: <br>
<br>
&quot;Hail Ergrez Shortpaw&quot;. He will not respond so you ask, &quot;what armor?&quot; <br>
<br>
Ergrez Shortpaw says &quot;Many armors. All of animal hides from the islands. If you wanting armor then I can make for you. All I ask is you do me favor.&quot; <br>
<br>
You say &quot;What favor?&quot; <br>
<br>
Ergrez Shortpaw says &quot;Snowfangs in need of much help lately. Once we mighty but now weak. You help us get stronger. If you want armor of wolves or cougar than I need, you bring twice as many materials. For each thing you wanting I need thing. Just tell me what furs you have and I tell you what I need.&quot; <br>
<br>
Ask &quot;What skin?&quot; <br>
<br>
Ergrez Shortpaw says &quot;Yes. I take skin of animal that hunters catch and make into things. Very important, very big job for clan.&quot; <br>
<br>
Then you have to tell him what skin you have, in this case, &quot;I have high quality cougar skin.&quot; <br>
<br>
Ergrez Shortpaw growls loudly. &quot;I not like making things of cat fur. Smells bad, hurts nose. You want me to work with that you bring food, lots of food. You bring me mammoth meats.&quot; <br>
<br>
At this point, give him the skin, and the 2 mammoth meats (unstacked of course). <br>
<br>
It will say something about Ergrez working a while with the furs. It will NOT tell you that you gained experience, faction, or anything else. The mask will appear in your inventory. Ta-da... a nice lil' piece of nodrop face armor! <br>
